#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-14-ipad-ssh-setup.rst:8
msgid "iPad上でSSH環境を無料で整える方法（iSH + OpenSSH）"
msgstr "How to set up an SSH environment on iPad for free (iSH + OpenSSH)"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-14-ipad-ssh-setup.rst:10
msgid ""
"**無料アプリ iSH を使って、iPad上にSSH環境を構築する手順** をまとめました。 ここまででLinuxにzsh + neovim + "
"tmux での環境を整えてきたのでSSH接続さえ確立できれば、いつでも作業が可能になります。"
msgstr ""
"**Steps to build an SSH environment on an iPad using the free app iSH**. Up "
"to this point, we have set up an environment with zsh + neovim + tmux on "
"Linux, so as long as we can establish an SSH connection, we can work at any "
"time."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-14-ipad-ssh-setup.rst:18
msgid "背景と目的"
msgstr "Background and purpose"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-14-ipad-ssh-setup.rst:20
msgid ""
"iPadには標準でターミナルが存在しないため、Linux的な作業やSSH経由でのポートフォワーディングを行うには工夫が必要です。 有料アプリ（Blink"
" ShellやTermius Pro）もありますが、**無料で完結したい** という場面では、iSHの活用が有力な選択肢です。"
msgstr ""
"Since the iPad does not have a terminal by default, some ingenuity is "
"required to perform Linux-like tasks and port forwarding via SSH. There are "
"paid apps (Blink Shell and Termius Pro), but in situations where you want to"
" complete the process for free, using iSH is a strong option."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-14-ipad-ssh-setup.rst:24
msgid "使用するツール"
msgstr "Tools used"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-14-ipad-ssh-setup.rst:26
msgid "**iSH** （App Storeから無料で入手可能）"
msgstr "**iSH** (Available for free from the App Store)"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-14-ipad-ssh-setup.rst:27
msgid "**OpenSSH** （Alpineパッケージとして追加）"
msgstr "**OpenSSH** (added as Alpine package)"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-14-ipad-ssh-setup.rst:29
msgid "iSHはAlpine Linuxに類似した軽量仮想環境であり、パッケージ管理に`apk`を使用します。"
msgstr ""
"iSH is a lightweight virtual environment similar to Alpine Linux that uses "
"`apk` for package management."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-14-ipad-ssh-setup.rst:32
msgid "導入手順"
msgstr "Installation steps"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-14-ipad-ssh-setup.rst:34
msgid "**iSHをApp Storeからインストール**"
msgstr "**Install iSH from the App Store**"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-14-ipad-ssh-setup.rst:35
msgid "iSHを起動し、次のコマンドを実行："
msgstr "Start iSH and run the following command:"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-14-ipad-ssh-setup.rst:42
msgid "これで `ssh`, `scp`, `sftp` などのコマンドが利用可能になります。"
msgstr "Commands such as `ssh`, `scp`, and `sftp` are now available."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-14-ipad-ssh-setup.rst:44
msgid "SSH接続してみる："
msgstr "Try connecting via SSH:"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-14-ipad-ssh-setup.rst:50
msgid "必要に応じて `.ssh/config` を整備して、接続先を整理することも可能です。"
msgstr ""
"If necessary, you can organize `.ssh/config` to organize the connection "
"destinations."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-14-ipad-ssh-setup.rst:53
msgid "ポートフォワーディング（ローカルトンネル）"
msgstr "Port forwarding (local tunnel)"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-14-ipad-ssh-setup.rst:55
msgid "iSH内で以下のように実行すれば、iPadローカルでポートフォワーディングが利用できます："
msgstr ""
"You can use port forwarding locally on your iPad by running the following "
"within iSH:"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-14-ipad-ssh-setup.rst:61
msgid "iPad側の `localhost:8080` にアクセスすると、リモートホストの `localhost:8000` にトンネルされます。"
msgstr ""
"When you access `localhost:8080` on the iPad side, it will be tunneled to "
"`localhost:8000` on the remote host."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-14-ipad-ssh-setup.rst:63
msgid "これで、リモートホストで簡易的に動作中のWebサーバにもアクセス可能になります。"
msgstr "Now you can easily access a web server running on a remote host."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-14-ipad-ssh-setup.rst:66
msgid "viで抜けられないときの対処"
msgstr "What to do when you can't exit with vi"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-14-ipad-ssh-setup.rst:68
msgid ""
"iPadなどのタブレットキーボードでは、`vi` などのエディタを起動した際に `ESC` キーが見つからず困ることがあります。 iPadでは次の操作で"
" `ESC` の代用が可能であることを知っておくと良いです。："
msgstr ""
"On a tablet keyboard such as an iPad, you may have trouble finding the `ESC`"
" key when starting an editor such as `vi`. It is good to know that on iPad, "
"you can substitute `ESC` with the following operation. :"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-14-ipad-ssh-setup.rst:71
msgid "ソフトウェアキーボード： ``Ctrl`` + ``[`` を押す"
msgstr "Software keyboard: press ``Ctrl`` + ``[``"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-14-ipad-ssh-setup.rst:75
msgid "色や表示のカスタマイズ"
msgstr "Customize colors and display"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-14-ipad-ssh-setup.rst:77
msgid "iSHはデフォルトでLightモードなので、好みに応じてダークモードへの変更も可能。"
msgstr ""
"iSH is in Light mode by default, so you can change to Dark mode if you "
"prefer."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-14-ipad-ssh-setup.rst:79
msgid "画面上部の「歯車アイコン」から変更できます。"
msgstr "You can change it from the \"gear icon\" at the top of the screen."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-14-ipad-ssh-setup.rst:82
msgid "まとめ"
msgstr "summary"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-14-ipad-ssh-setup.rst:84
msgid ""
"iSH + OpenSSH を使えば、iPad上でも軽快なターミナル環境が手に入ります。 ポートフォワーディングまで含めた機能を**無料で実現** "
"できる点が魅力です。"
msgstr ""
"By using iSH + OpenSSH, you can get a lightweight terminal environment even "
"on your iPad. Its appeal is that it provides functions including port "
"forwarding **for free**."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-14-ipad-ssh-setup.rst:87
msgid "接続先のLinux側ではzsh + neovim + tmuxといった環境が整って入れば、外出先で手軽にサイト管理ができそうです。"
msgstr ""
"If you have an environment like zsh + neovim + tmux installed on the "
"connected Linux side, you will be able to easily manage your site on the go."

